<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to ChatFlow</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f7fafc; font-family: 'Outfit', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f7fafc;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
                <table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; max-width: 100%;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 48px 32px;">
                            <!-- Header -->
                            <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 24px;">
                                        <h1 style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4ade80 0%, #d4d4f7 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; color: #4ade80; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; text-align: center;">
                                            ChatFlow
                                        </h1>
                                        <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 16px; margin: 8px 0 0 0; text-align: center;">
                                            Welcome to your new chat experience
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Content -->
                            <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        <h2 style="color: #262b33; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
                                            Hi {{name}},
                                        </h2>

                                        <p style="color: #374151; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                                            Thank you for joining ChatFlow! We're thrilled to have you as part of our community. Start connecting with friends, family, and colleagues through our intuitive and secure chat platform.
                                        </p>

                                        <p style="color: #374151; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                                            Here are a few things you can do to get started:
                                        </p>

                                        <ul style="color: #374151; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                                            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Complete your profile to personalize your experience</li>
                                            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Add friends using their username or email</li>
                                            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Create group chats for team collaboration</li>
                                            <li>Explore our features like file sharing and voice messages</li>
                                        </ul>

                                        <p style="color: #374151; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 32px 0;">
                                            If you have any questions or need help getting started, our support team is here to assist you.
                                        </p>

                                        <!-- CTA Button -->
                                        <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td align="center">
                                                    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #4ade80; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.3);">
                                                        Get Started
                                                    </a>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>

                                        <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 0 0;">
                                            Happy chatting!<br>
                                            The ChatFlow Team
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>